									<p>Massage cleanser onto damp skin, avoiding contact with eyes. rinse off with water and pat dry. can be used AM or PM.</p>

<p><strong>suggested routine&nbsp;</strong><br/>
<br/>
1. cleanse with AHA Jelly Cleanser<br/>
2. tone<br/>
3. serum<br/>
4. moisturizer<br/>
5. SPF (daytime)</p>

<p><strong>how to recycle</strong></p>

<ul>
	<li>Twist off the cap and cut open the top of the sugarcane tube. rinse well. toss tube in recycling bin (unfortunately, the cap is not recyclable due to its small size).</li>
</ul>

								
