    <span class="block w-full sm:w-fit text-p sm:text-p-bold !leading-relaxed text-secondary text-center pr-5 pl-7 sm:pl-2 !font-black lowercase"><strong>what is the difference between the oil to milk cleanser and the aha jelly cleanser?</strong></span>
